1
01:20:24,710 --> 01:20:27,760
Et si ça perd ? Alors ?

1
01:20:27,760 --> 01:20:31,260
Si ça perd, mon précieux,
nous le mangeons !

1
01:20:32,390 --> 01:20:36,180
Si Sacquet perd,
nous le mangeons tout entier.

1
01:20:42,730 --> 01:20:43,650
Entendu.

1
01:20:48,740 --> 01:20:51,070
Sacquet commence.

1
01:20:56,790 --> 01:20:59,500
<i>Trente chevaux blancs
sur une colline rouge.</i>

1
01:21:00,290 --> 01:21:03,080
<i>D'abord ils mâchent,
puis ils piaffent.</i>

1
01:21:03,170 --> 01:21:04,830
<i>Puis plus rien ne bouge.</i>

1
01:21:15,890 --> 01:21:17,850
Les dents ?

1
01:21:17,850 --> 01:21:21,980
Les dents ! Oui, mon précieux !

1
01:21:21,980 --> 01:21:28,070
Mais nous...
Nous n'en avons que neuf.

1
01:21:31,740 --> 01:21:32,860
À nous.

1
01:21:33,780 --> 01:21:36,530
<i>Sans voix, il hurle.</i>

1
01:21:37,080 --> 01:21:40,080
<i>Sans ailes, voltige.</i>

1
01:21:40,160 --> 01:21:42,750
<i>Sans dents, mord.</i>

1
01:21:43,460 --> 01:21:47,250
<i>Sans bouche, murmure.</i>

1
01:21:49,670 --> 01:21:51,630
